tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE BiopharmaceuticalProducts (
  product_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  product_name VARCHAR(255),
  manufacturer VARCHAR(255),
  distribution_facility VARCHAR(255),
  storage_conditions TEXT,
  storage_temperature DECIMAL,
  expiration_date DATE
)

CREATE TABLE Distribution (
id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
product_name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
quantity INT NOT NULL,
location VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
storage_conditions VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL
);

CREATE TABLE Storage (
id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
location VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
temperature FLOAT NOT NULL,
humidity FLOAT NOT NULL,
last_updated TIMESTAMP NOT NULL
);

CREATE TABLE product_distribution (
    distribution_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    product_id INT,
    center_id INT,
    distribution_date DATE,
    quantity INT
);

CREATE TABLE DistributionCenters (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    name VARCHAR(255),
    location VARCHAR(255),
    capacity INT
)

CREATE TABLE Products (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    name VARCHAR(255),
    description TEXT,
    storage_condition VARCHAR(255)
)

CREATE TABLE Shipments (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    product_id INT,
    from_center_id INT,
    to_center_id INT,
    quantity INT,
    timestamp TIMESTAMP
)

CREATE TABLE QualityControl (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    product_id INT,
    center_id INT,
    temperature FLOAT,
    humidity FLOAT,
    FOREIGN KEY (product_id) REFERENCES Products(id),
    FOREIGN KEY (center_id) REFERENCES DistributionCenters(id)
)

CREATE TABLE Shipments (
    shipment_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    product_id INT,
    distribution_center_id INT,
    quantity INT NOT NULL,
    shipment_date DATE NOT NULL
);

CREATE TABLE QualityControl (
    qc_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    product_id INT,
    distribution_center_id INT,
    temperature FLOAT NOT NULL,
    humidity FLOAT NOT NULL
);

CREATE TABLE TrackingLogs (
    log_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    product_id INT,
    distribution_center_id INT,
    action VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
    log_date TIMESTAMP NOT NULL
);
